{"tid":1938258,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警 : 銅鑼灣拘捕一男一女 涉行為不檢挑釁警員 藏有攻擊性武器(鐳射筆)","createTime":"2020-03-22T12:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T14:37:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb7f26e692912e51583cc27516623beaee916ea","tid":1938258,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"警方昨晚於銅鑼灣拘捕兩人 涉行為不檢及藏攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n昨日是元朗721暴力襲擊事件發生8個月，全港多處有人聚集，警方在銅鑼灣時代廣場拘捕一男一女。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，昨晚當聚集人士離開期間，一名54歲男子大聲喧嘩並煽動在場人士的情緒，並以粗言穢語挑釁警員，以涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢，將他拘捕；警方同時在一名16歲少女身上檢獲一支鐳射筆，她涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275665&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275665%26csid%3D261_341&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdMhAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=ac1f587e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275665&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"662a442efe423c0d8150f74d9094c33ab287b280","tid":1938258,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />惡過皇軍"},{"pid":"48faa0365b4cd89482d079973f2cea7a88c847f8","tid":1938258,"uid":76745,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"鬧都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27007b4e471e21420cf0257ca81f1c2a6e67fa9","tid":1938258,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:10:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"764d6cf3f50962d8cf0bf035c3ad244c173bbaf7","tid":1938258,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:10:51.000Z","msg":"唔駛辱狗罪啦，公眾地方行為不檢同當年不誠實使用電腦萬能key一樣<br />\n<br />\n鐳射筆一日未打到終審兩邊都有勝訴機會"},{"pid":"5fe52c4df307b3f3b01c8687545b625930b4509d","tid":1938258,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"